level is represented by a numeric value where lower numbers indicate higher urgency.\n* Arrival time is recorded 
as a timestamp.\n* Sorting applies to the entire patient queue.\n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n\n```gherkin\nGiven 
the patient queue contains multiple patients with different urgency levels and arrival times\nWhen the queue is 
